Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:38.43,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\frz270\pos(1265,360)}四散的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:45.68,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\frz270\pos(1265,360)}记忆的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:54.02,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\frz270\pos(1265,360)}独自一人渴求着
